WEBVTT

00:10.534 --> 00:11.531
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "GREENLEAF..."</i>

00:11.533 --> 00:14.332
I DON'T KNOW WHY H&H
HID FROM MY BROTHER

00:14.334 --> 00:17.665
AND FROM ME AND CALVARY THAT
THEY'RE BUYING UP ALL THIS LAND.

00:17.667 --> 00:20.198
WE WANT TO PUT CALVARY
ON THE MAP.

00:20.200 --> 00:23.332
YOU SEE? IT HAS ALL THE EVIDENCE
YOU NEED RIGHT THERE.

00:23.334 --> 00:24.865
HMM.

00:24.867 --> 00:26.932
H&H IS PAYING OFF
CONNIE SYKES.

00:26.934 --> 00:28.765
THAT IS WHAT THEY DO.

00:28.767 --> 00:31.432
THEY SLOWLY GET CONTROL
OF THE CHURCH.

00:31.434 --> 00:33.298
BUT WE STILL HAVE
HALF THE SEATS.

00:33.300 --> 00:35.965
YES, BUT IF THEY GET
THOSE 12 SEATS,

00:35.967 --> 00:38.332
WHO WILL THOSE
12 PEOPLE BE ANYHOW?

00:38.334 --> 00:41.765
NOW, IF YOU WERE MINE,
I'D MADE SURE YOU WERE
ALWAYS TAKEN CARE OF.

00:41.767 --> 00:42.732
I DIDN'T DO IT.

00:42.734 --> 00:45.165
YEAH, I KNOW.
BUT I JUST LIED TO THE POLICE.

00:45.167 --> 00:46.898
THAT IS NOT IDEAL.

00:46.900 --> 00:48.098
SHE'S LYING.

00:48.100 --> 00:49.765
BOO-YAH.

00:49.767 --> 00:51.665
YOU WANT TO GO FOR A RIDE?
WHERE?

00:51.667 --> 00:53.532
COOL JUST TO DRIVE
SOMETIMES, YOU KNOW?

00:53.534 --> 00:56.132
James: WE WOULD LIKE YOU
TO PUT THINGS ON HOLD

00:56.134 --> 00:58.265
UNTIL GRACE BECOMES
PERMANENT HEAD PASTOR.

00:58.267 --> 01:00.432
GRACE FIRST...

01:00.434 --> 01:02.498
[SIGHS] THEN ME.

01:02.500 --> 01:03.632
SEND BOB THE RECORDING.

01:03.634 --> 01:05.898
WRITE THE E-MAIL, WHATEVER.
JUST DO IT.

01:05.900 --> 01:08.598
IT'S TIME THAT SISTER
OF MINE PAID.

01:08.600 --> 01:12.532
♪♪

01:12.534 --> 01:13.898
CLARA...

01:13.900 --> 01:16.565
NO ONE SHARES YOUR CONCERN
FOR THE HISTORY OF THIS CHURCH

01:16.567 --> 01:19.465
AND ITS INDEPENDENCE
MORE THAN I DO,

01:19.467 --> 01:21.999
BUT I PROMISE YOU
HARMONY AND HOPE

01:22.001 --> 01:25.598
HAVING SEATS ON THIS BOARD
WILL NOT ENDANGER THAT.

01:25.600 --> 01:27.598
12 SEATS, THOUGH, PASTOR.

01:27.600 --> 01:29.265
IT'S STILL JUST 50%.

01:29.267 --> 01:32.798
WHAT JUDEE MEANS, CLARA,
IS THAT WITH US HAVING 12

01:32.800 --> 01:35.065
AND HARMONY AND HOPE
HAVING 12,

01:35.067 --> 01:39.932
EVERYTHING WOULD ALWAYS BE
A CONVERSATION BETWEEN FRIENDS.

01:39.934 --> 01:41.965
AND WHAT ABOUT
WHAT MAE SAID?

01:41.967 --> 01:43.998
WHERE'S THE ROOM
FOR GOD IN THAT?

01:44.000 --> 01:48.198
CLARA, H&H IS WILLING
TO POUR MILLIONS OF DOLLARS

01:48.200 --> 01:51.099
INTO OUR CHURCH,
BUT THEY WILL NOT DO THAT

01:51.101 --> 01:54.332
IF WE DON'T GIVE THEM
THESE BOARD SEATS.

01:54.334 --> 01:57.332
THAT'S THE SITUATION.

01:57.334 --> 01:59.131
WELL, ALRIGHT, THEN.

01:59.133 --> 02:01.798
WELL, I'LL SEE Y'ALL
AT THE MEETING,

02:01.800 --> 02:03.932
AND I'LL VOTE YES,
BUT I'M --

02:03.934 --> 02:06.865
WE PROMISE
YOU WON'T REGRET IT.

02:06.867 --> 02:10.065
NOW, DON'T PROMISE ME.
JUST MAKE SURE THAT I DON'T.

02:10.067 --> 02:11.598
THAT'LL BE ENOUGH FOR ME.

02:11.600 --> 02:12.865
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:12.867 --> 02:15.031
HERE WE GO, GRANDMA.
I'LL WALK YOU OUT TO YOUR CAR.

02:15.033 --> 02:17.765
OH, ISN'T KARINE
JUST WONDERFUL?

02:17.767 --> 02:18.898
OH, YES.

02:18.900 --> 02:20.665
SHE'S AN ABSOLUTE ANGEL.
GOOD TO SEE YOU.

02:23.633 --> 02:26.465
WELL...

02:26.467 --> 02:28.365
I BELIEVE WE'VE MET WITH ALL
THE DEACONS AT THIS POINT.

02:28.367 --> 02:29.431
AM I RIGHT, CONNIE?

02:29.433 --> 02:31.332
HMM. EXCEPT FOR ME.

02:31.334 --> 02:34.598
OH. [ LAUGHS ] FUNNY!

02:34.600 --> 02:36.532
WELL, THEN THE VOTE'S
IN THE BAG.

02:36.534 --> 02:38.265
OR IT HAD BETTER BE, ANYHOW.

02:38.267 --> 02:40.598
OTHERWISE, DADDY'S GOING
TO BE VERY, VERY UPSET.

02:40.600 --> 02:41.665
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:50.900 --> 02:54.632
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

03:02.334 --> 03:03.798
HEY, MAMA.

03:03.800 --> 03:04.865
HOW DID IT GO?

03:04.867 --> 03:06.665
CLARA JACKSON JUST LEFT.

03:06.667 --> 03:08.998
AND SHE SAID
SHE'D VOTE YES?

03:09.000 --> 03:10.132
SHE DID.

03:10.134 --> 03:13.265
OH. WELL, YOUR FATHER
IS ON HIS WAY

03:13.267 --> 03:15.732
OVER TO CONNIE'S NOW
TO INTERCEPT HER.

03:15.734 --> 03:17.265
IS HE GOING TO TELL HER
THAT WE KNOW?

03:17.267 --> 03:22.265
NO, ABOUT THE H&H PAYMENT?
NO. I FORBID THEM TO DO SO.

03:22.267 --> 03:24.665
HE'S GOING TO APPEAL
TO HER REASON.

03:24.667 --> 03:25.531
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:25.533 --> 03:26.665
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

03:26.667 --> 03:28.065
PASTOR GREENLEAF.

03:28.067 --> 03:30.798
I GOT TO RUN.

03:30.800 --> 03:33.665
PASTOR DEMARS.

03:33.667 --> 03:36.032
HOW CAN I HELP?

03:36.034 --> 03:38.298
BY RESIGNING.

03:38.300 --> 03:39.598
EXCUSE ME?

03:39.600 --> 03:41.465
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:41.467 --> 03:43.132
IS THAT A JOKE?

03:43.134 --> 03:45.798
I HAVE PROOF...

03:45.800 --> 03:50.665
YOU LIED...TO KEEP YOUR SON
OUT OF JAIL.

03:50.667 --> 03:54.398
IF YOU STEP DOWN, I WON'T SHARE
THIS PROOF WITH THE POLICE.

03:54.400 --> 03:57.732
IF YOU REFUSE TO STEP DOWN,
I WILL SHARE IT WITH THEM.

03:57.734 --> 04:00.998
AND UPON HEARING IT, I EXPECT
THEY'LL REOPEN HIS CASE

04:01.000 --> 04:04.198
AND THE WHEELS OF JUSTICE
WILL BEGIN TO...

04:04.200 --> 04:05.665
ROLL OVER YOU BOTH.

04:05.667 --> 04:08.465
YOU HAVE UNTIL SUNDAY
TO DECIDE.

04:08.467 --> 04:17.031
♪♪

04:17.033 --> 04:18.998
GOD IS GOOD.

04:19.000 --> 04:26.865
♪♪

04:26.867 --> 04:34.798
♪♪

04:34.800 --> 04:36.265
[ SIGHS ]

04:36.267 --> 04:38.665
♪ AMEN ♪

04:41.167 --> 04:42.498
♪ ALL RIGHT ♪

04:42.500 --> 04:43.732
♪ AMEN ♪

04:43.734 --> 04:46.698
♪ UH-HUH, HMM ♪

04:46.700 --> 04:49.232
♪ OOH-OOH, OOH ♪

04:52.334 --> 04:53.699
♪ WELL ♪

04:57.134 --> 05:00.265
♪ OH-OHH, OHH ♪

05:00.267 --> 05:05.598
♪ OOH, OOH, OOH, OOH ♪

05:05.600 --> 05:08.632
♪ AMEN, AMEN ♪
♪ OH ♪

05:12.067 --> 05:13.865
♪ YEAH ♪

05:13.867 --> 05:16.865
-- Captions by VITAC --
 www.vitac.com

05:16.867 --> 05:19.932
CAPTIONS PAID FOR BY
DISCOVERY COMMUNICATIONS

05:19.934 --> 05:24.098
♪♪

05:25.200 --> 05:29.265
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
WEARING THAT THING?

05:29.267 --> 05:32.532
HEADING OVER TO BUCKETS,
DANTE'S NEW SPORTS BAR.

05:32.534 --> 05:34.465
HE'S STILL ON
YOUR TO-DO LIST?

05:34.467 --> 05:36.598
[ CHUCKLES ] YEAH, HE IS.
[ GROANS ]

05:36.600 --> 05:38.065
LAST TIME WE SAW
EACH OTHER, THOUGH,

05:38.067 --> 05:39.198
IT KIND OF ENDED BADLY.

05:39.200 --> 05:40.932
WHY? DID YOU GET IN HIS FACE
AND TELL HIM ABOUT

05:40.934 --> 05:44.598
HOW HE LOST YOU BOTH OF YOUR
JOBS WITH HIS GRANDSTANDING?

05:44.600 --> 05:47.732
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.
LOOK, I GOT TO GO.

05:47.734 --> 05:50.665
[ SIGHS ] JACOB.

05:50.667 --> 05:51.732
YEAH?

05:51.734 --> 05:53.532
BEFORE YOU GO,

05:53.534 --> 05:56.265
WILL YOU PLEASE ASK YOUR MOTHER
ABOUT THE HOUSE?

05:56.267 --> 05:58.099
I TOLD YOU I DON'T WANT TO ASK
HER ABOUT THAT. IT'S RUDE.

05:58.101 --> 06:01.098
PEOPLE HAVE WILLS.
PEOPLE HAVE CHILDREN.

06:01.100 --> 06:02.432
IT IS NOT RUDE TO ASK.

06:02.434 --> 06:04.165
IT SEEMS KIND OF RUDE TO ME.

06:04.167 --> 06:06.232
WE'RE NOT STANDING AROUND
TAPPING OUR FEET,

06:06.234 --> 06:07.698
WAITING FOR PEOPLE TO DIE.

06:07.700 --> 06:10.832
WE JUST WANT TO SELL OUR SHARE
IN THE HOUSE IF WE HAVE ONE.

06:10.834 --> 06:12.698
JUST ASK.

06:12.700 --> 06:13.832
I MEAN, IF WE'RE EVER
GOING TO WIN

06:13.834 --> 06:15.965
ONE OF THESE BIDDING WARS
ON A HOUSE, WE NEED MORE CASH.

06:15.967 --> 06:17.499
I'M HAPPY LIVING HERE,
KERISSA.

06:17.501 --> 06:19.232
AND I'M NOT,
AND YOU KNOW THAT.

06:19.234 --> 06:21.765
THEN YOU ASK HER.

06:21.767 --> 06:23.365
I'LL PRAY FOR YOU.

06:23.367 --> 06:26.198
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

06:26.200 --> 06:27.232
[ SIGHS ]

06:28.600 --> 06:33.332
♪♪

06:33.334 --> 06:35.865
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

06:35.867 --> 06:38.965
CONNIE.

06:38.967 --> 06:40.432
[ SIGHS ]

06:40.434 --> 06:42.665
I ASSUME YOU'RE HERE
ABOUT THE VOTE,

06:42.667 --> 06:45.398
AS IF MAE'S LITTLE SERMON
AT YOUR RE-ENGAGEMENT PARTY

06:45.400 --> 06:46.798
WASN'T EMBARRASSING ENOUGH.

06:46.800 --> 06:50.065
WHEN WILL YOU TO REALIZE
THAT YOU ARE UNINVOLVED?

06:50.067 --> 06:52.332
WE BUILT THIS CHURCH
FROM THE GROUND UP,

06:52.334 --> 06:54.198
AND YOU'RE ABOUT TO HAND
TOTAL CONTROL OF ITS FUTURE

06:54.200 --> 06:57.032
TO A BUNCH OF
CARPET BAGGERS WITH BIBLES.

06:57.034 --> 06:58.665
GRACE IS IN FAVOR
OF THE PLAN.

06:58.667 --> 07:00.465
GRACE IS IN THE GRIP
OF AMBITION.

07:00.467 --> 07:03.598
GRACE IS ON THE VERGE
OF MARCHING THE CHURCH

07:03.600 --> 07:06.798
YOU ALMOST DESTROYED
INTO THE PAGES OF HISTORY.

07:06.800 --> 07:09.532
SPEAKING OF THOSE PAGES --

07:09.534 --> 07:11.665
DON'T START WITH ONE
OF YOUR POLYSYLLABIC

07:11.667 --> 07:13.265
WORD PARADES, JAMES.

07:13.267 --> 07:15.165
I DON'T HAVE TO LISTEN
ANYMORE.

07:15.167 --> 07:16.699
YOU KNOW, I WASN'T GOING TO
BRING THIS UP,

07:16.701 --> 07:20.165
BUT WHERE DO YOU THINK
THE CHAPTER WILL BE, CONNIE,

07:20.167 --> 07:21.565
IN THOSE PAGES OF HISTORY

07:21.567 --> 07:26.698
ABOUT HOW YOU TOOK A BRIBE
TO HAND CALVARY OVER TO H&H --

07:26.700 --> 07:28.565
AT THE END OF THE BOOK,

07:28.567 --> 07:33.132
OR WILL IT HAVE ITS OWN
LITTLE...PAMPHLET?

07:33.134 --> 07:35.665
YOU CAN'T SEEM
TO ACCEPT IT, CAN YOU --

07:35.667 --> 07:38.465
THAT REASONABLE PEOPLE
LOOKED ON YOUR WORKS

07:38.467 --> 07:39.865
AND FOUND THEM WANTING?

07:39.867 --> 07:43.065
OH, NO. YOU WANT TO MAKE IT
SOME BIG CONSPIRACY.

07:43.067 --> 07:44.732
NOT A BIG ONE.

07:44.734 --> 07:46.865
JUST ONE FAT CHECK

07:46.867 --> 07:48.932
WRITTEN ON APRIL 2nd

07:48.934 --> 07:51.132
FROM A HARMONY & HOPE
BUSINESS ACCOUNT,

07:51.134 --> 07:53.332
DEPOSITED ON APRIL 5th
INTO TO YOUR ACCOUNT

07:53.334 --> 07:54.998
AT THE CHURCH CREDIT UNION,

07:55.000 --> 07:57.198
THEN PAID OUT
THE VERY NEXT DAY

07:57.200 --> 08:00.465
TO YOUR DAUGHTER,
WHOM, I ASSUME,

08:00.467 --> 08:04.332
IS HOLDING IT FOR YOU
UNTIL ALL THIS BLOWS OVER

08:04.334 --> 08:06.465
AND ANYONE
WHO COULD HAVE KNOWN...

08:06.467 --> 08:08.465
IS GONE.

08:08.467 --> 08:14.598
I AM NOT GOING TO DIGNIFY
THIS MADNESS WITH A DENIAL.

08:14.600 --> 08:16.065
WHAT WOULD BE THE POINT?

08:16.067 --> 08:18.065
YOU ARE OBVIOUSLY --
THE CONGREGATION

08:18.067 --> 08:21.665
WILL MAINTAIN MAJORITY
LEADERSHIP OF THE BOARD

08:21.667 --> 08:24.598
OR EVERYONE WILL FIND OUT.

08:24.600 --> 08:26.798
EV'RYBODY.

08:26.800 --> 08:33.998
♪♪

08:34.000 --> 08:42.332
♪♪

08:42.334 --> 08:43.732
I CAN HEAR YOU.

08:43.734 --> 08:45.532
HAVE YOU PRINTED OUT THAT COPY
OF THE CHURCH BYLAWS

08:45.534 --> 08:48.132
I ASKED YOU FOR LAST WEEK
TWICE AND YESTERDAY?

08:48.134 --> 08:49.531
I'LL GET RIGHT ON IT.

08:49.533 --> 08:53.131
THAT'S WHAT YOU SAID LAST WEEK
TWICE AND YESTERDAY.

08:53.133 --> 08:55.198
SHOULD I TELL PASTOR
WHAT A RESISTANT LITTLE CAMPER

08:55.200 --> 08:57.598
SHE'S GOT ON HER HANDS?

08:57.600 --> 08:59.532
NO, MISS WHITMORE.

08:59.534 --> 09:01.865
THEN HOW ABOUT YOU
JUST PRINT IT?

09:01.867 --> 09:03.332
IF I LEAVE THE PAGE I'M ON,

09:03.334 --> 09:05.332
I'M GOING TO LOSE
YOUR AMY GRANT TICKETS.

09:05.334 --> 09:07.332
YOU FOUND SOME?
I DID.

09:07.334 --> 09:08.732
OKAY.

09:08.734 --> 09:10.532
BUT PRINT IT AFTER THAT.

09:10.534 --> 09:13.798
YES, MA'AM.

09:13.800 --> 09:17.065
I'M NOT GOING TO SAY THANK YOU
UNTIL IT ACTUALLY HAPPENS,

09:17.067 --> 09:18.465
JUST FYI.

09:18.467 --> 09:19.932
YOU'RE WELCOME.

09:25.067 --> 09:26.765
WHO WILL INHERENT MY HOUSE?

09:26.767 --> 09:28.965
I KNOW IT'S CONSIDERED
UNSEEMLY BY SOME

09:28.967 --> 09:30.365
TO ASK SUCH A QUESTION,
BUT...

09:30.367 --> 09:32.498
I'D SAY MOST, IF NOT ALL.

09:32.500 --> 09:34.232
...IN ORDER FOR JACOB AND I
TO BE EFFECTIVE

09:34.234 --> 09:36.332
IN THIS HOUSING MARKET,
WE NEED MORE CASH.

09:36.334 --> 09:38.665
YOU DON'T KNOW, MAE.
IT'S CRAZY OUT THERE.

09:38.667 --> 09:41.265
WELL, IT'S NOT
COMPLETELY SANE IN HERE.

09:41.267 --> 09:43.332
WHY, JUST THE OTHER NIGHT
I HAD TO CLEAR OUT MY SAFE

09:43.334 --> 09:46.398
JUST TO MAKE SURE IT WASN'T
JACKED BY MY SON'S WIFE.

09:46.400 --> 09:48.598
YEAH? WELL, I GOT
SLAPPED IN THE FACE

09:48.600 --> 09:51.065
BY MY MOTHER-IN-LAW,
SO IT'S TOUGH ALL OVER.

09:51.067 --> 09:55.065
WHO GETS THE HOUSE?

09:55.067 --> 09:56.865
THE HOUSE
WILL BE LEFT TO --

09:56.867 --> 09:59.998
AND I TELL YOU THIS BECAUSE
IT'S PAINFULLY OBVIOUS,

10:00.000 --> 10:02.098
OR WOULD BE TO ANYONE
WHO WASN'T SO BLINDED

10:02.100 --> 10:05.432
BY GREED AND DESPERATION --

10:05.434 --> 10:09.332
TO GRACE, JACOB, AND CHARITY

10:09.334 --> 10:10.598
EQUALLY.

10:10.600 --> 10:14.265
♪♪

10:14.267 --> 10:16.198
[ SIGHS ]

10:16.200 --> 10:17.732
♪♪

10:17.734 --> 10:18.998
WHAT IS THIS PROOF PHIL HAS?

10:19.000 --> 10:21.132
OF WHAT?
STOP LYING TO ME.

10:21.134 --> 10:24.099
WHAT PROOF DOES PHIL HAVE
THAT I LIED TO THE POLICE?

10:24.101 --> 10:26.832
GRACE, PHIL AND I DON'T TALK
ABOUT WORK WHEN WE'RE OFF.

10:26.834 --> 10:31.332
WE DON'T TALK ABOUT US AT WORK.
CHINESE WALLS.

10:31.334 --> 10:34.332
IF THEY FIND OUT THAT I LIED,
A.J. COULD GO BACK TO PRISON.

10:34.334 --> 10:35.665
JUST TELL ME
WHAT YOU TOLD PHIL --

10:35.667 --> 10:38.298
WHAT HE HAS,
WHAT HE THINKS THAT HE HAS.

10:38.300 --> 10:40.232
TELL ME.
I DON'T KNOW.

10:40.234 --> 10:42.332
CHARITY, HE IS MY SON.

10:44.967 --> 10:47.399
I DON'T KNOW WHAT PHIL HAS.

10:53.934 --> 10:56.965
YOU KNOW, WHATEVER IT IS
THAT YOU ARE ANGRY ABOUT,

10:56.967 --> 10:58.765
WHATEVER THIS WHOLE THING
THAT YOU'RE DOING,

10:58.767 --> 11:01.732
WHATEVER YOU THINK
THAT IT'S GOING TO GET YOU,

11:01.734 --> 11:04.532
IS IT REALLY WORTH RUINING
A WHOLE NOTHER PERSON'S LIFE?

11:04.534 --> 11:08.998
GRACE,
YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE LIED.

11:09.000 --> 11:10.998
THAT'S YOUR ANSWER?

11:11.000 --> 11:12.131
SERIOUSLY?

11:12.133 --> 11:15.798
I HAVEN'T DONE ANYTHING,
GRACE.

11:15.800 --> 11:18.332
YOU BROUGHT ALL THIS ON
YOURSELF.

11:18.334 --> 11:22.498
♪♪

11:22.500 --> 11:24.598
[ SCOFFS ]

11:24.600 --> 11:31.998
♪♪

11:32.000 --> 11:35.665
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

11:35.667 --> 11:37.832
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

11:42.834 --> 11:45.698
♪♪

11:45.700 --> 11:48.865
HOW'S IT GOING WITH CHARITY?

11:48.867 --> 11:51.265
IS THAT WHY YOU PARKED
YOURSELF THERE FOR AN HOUR --

11:51.267 --> 11:52.798
TO ASK ME THAT?

11:52.800 --> 11:56.865
I AM WAITING FOR KARINE TO
GET ME MY AMY GRANT TICKETS...

11:56.867 --> 11:59.032
AND THE BYLAWS
TO THIS CIRCUS.

12:01.934 --> 12:05.332
IT'S GOING VERY WELL,
THANK YOU.

12:05.334 --> 12:07.132
YOU DON'T...

12:07.134 --> 12:10.265
REALLY LOVE HER,
DO YOU?

12:10.267 --> 12:11.265
WHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT?

12:11.267 --> 12:13.465
SHE'S KIND OF
NOTHING LIKE ME.

12:13.467 --> 12:15.065
YOU TWO ARE A LOT
ALIKE, ACTUALLY.

12:15.067 --> 12:16.931
BOY, I CAN'T WAIT
TO HEAR HOW.

12:16.933 --> 12:18.398
YOU'RE BOTH DAUGHTERS
OF POWERFUL MEN

12:18.400 --> 12:20.632
WHO FEEL THEY'VE NEVER GOTTEN
THE RESPECT THEY DESERVE.

12:20.634 --> 12:23.932
YOU BOTH ARE ADORABLY NOISY
WHEN YOU DON'T GET YOUR WAY.

12:23.934 --> 12:24.998
YOU BOTH ARE --

12:25.000 --> 12:26.432
SO, IT'S BECAUSE
SHE'S BLACK?

12:26.434 --> 12:27.432
CAREFUL.

12:27.434 --> 12:30.132
WELL, YOU SAY
SHE'S JUST LIKE ME,

12:30.134 --> 12:32.732
BUT IN ONE BIG WAY,
SHE'S NOT.

12:32.734 --> 12:35.132
SHE'S BLACK.
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:35.134 --> 12:36.865
YOU'RE AT THE POINT IN YOUR LIFE
WHERE YOU FEEL LIKE YOU NEED

12:36.867 --> 12:40.131
TO BE WITH A BLACK WOMAN.
IT'S A THING.

12:40.133 --> 12:42.131
WE'RE JUST TALKING
AS FRIENDS.

12:42.133 --> 12:44.265
JUDEE...

12:44.267 --> 12:47.799
I'M SORRY THINGS ARE TOUGH FOR
YOU AND KEN RIGHT NOW, REALLY.

12:47.801 --> 12:49.132
WHY EVEN SAY THAT?

12:49.134 --> 12:51.465
NEITHER THING HAS ONE THING TO
DO WITH THE OTHER THING.

12:51.467 --> 12:53.998
TWO, THANKS.
IT'S NOT A THING.

12:54.000 --> 12:55.932
SHE'S A PERSON -- A PERSON
I CARE ABOUT VERY MUCH,

12:55.934 --> 12:58.265
A PERSON WHO'S GOING TO BE
A BIG PART OF THIS CHURCH

12:58.267 --> 12:59.732
ONCE GRACE IS GONE.

13:02.667 --> 13:04.065
WELL, LET'S HAVE DINNER.

13:04.067 --> 13:05.932
I CAN'T IMAGINE
ANYTHING WORSE.

13:05.934 --> 13:10.199
NO! IF SHE'S SO GREAT
AND WE ARE SO MUCH ALIKE...

13:10.201 --> 13:11.731
LET'S HAVE DINNER.

13:11.733 --> 13:13.798
IN FACT, IF YOU WANT
MY HELP PAVING THE WAY FOR HER

13:13.800 --> 13:16.532
WITH DADDY IN THIS BEAUTIFUL,
BLACK FUTURE OF YOURS --

13:16.534 --> 13:18.665
AND YOU'RE
GOING TO NEED IT --

13:18.667 --> 13:20.265
I'D SET THAT DINNER.

13:20.267 --> 13:22.399
I'M FREE TOMORROW.

13:22.401 --> 13:24.532
I'LL SEE
IF SHE'S AVAILABLE.

13:24.534 --> 13:28.432
OH, DON'T WORRY.
I KNOW I'M JEALOUS.

13:28.434 --> 13:30.465
I WOULD NEVER ACTUALLY
DO ANYTHING

13:30.467 --> 13:32.665
TO STOP YOU
FROM BEING HAPPY, PHIL.

13:32.667 --> 13:34.532
OH, I PRAY THAT'S TRUE,
FOR YOUR SAKE.

13:34.534 --> 13:36.165
POINT TAKEN.

13:42.000 --> 13:43.332
OH.

13:43.334 --> 13:45.798
ONE QUESTION, THOUGH.

13:45.800 --> 13:47.465
WHAT?

13:47.467 --> 13:49.032
WHAT MAKES YOU SO SURE

13:49.034 --> 13:53.231
GRACE ISN'T GOING TO BE
DADDY'S LONG-TERM PICK?

13:53.233 --> 13:55.032
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK
HE'LL DO?

13:55.034 --> 13:57.399
NO ONE EVER KNOWS WHAT DADDY
IS GOING TO DO,

13:57.401 --> 14:00.932
BUT WHAT MAKES YOU SO SURE
IT ISN'T GOING TO GO THAT WAY?

14:00.934 --> 14:04.265
LET'S JUST SAY...
I HAVE A FEELING.

14:04.267 --> 14:05.732
INTERESTING.

14:05.734 --> 14:09.398
SO MANY FEELINGS.

14:09.400 --> 14:11.998
I'M FEELING STEAK.

14:12.000 --> 14:13.565
JUST SAYING.

14:16.800 --> 14:25.865
♪♪

14:25.867 --> 14:27.899
HEY, MAN.
HEY. HOW YOU DOING?

14:27.901 --> 14:29.799
[ GAME BEEPING ]

14:29.801 --> 14:32.065
PASTOR GREENLEAF.

14:32.067 --> 14:33.398
BROTHER GREENLEAF NOW, MAN.

14:33.400 --> 14:35.798
HEY, GIVE ME A SEC, MAN.
I'M TRYING TO SET A SCORE

14:35.800 --> 14:37.465
ON THIS GAME
THAT'LL NEVER BE BROKEN.

14:37.467 --> 14:38.732
ALRIGHT.

14:38.734 --> 14:40.798
[ SHOUTS INDISTINCTLY ]

14:40.800 --> 14:42.798
1,900, BABY!
[ BUZZER SOUNDS ]

14:42.800 --> 14:44.798
THAT'LL NEVER BE TOPPED.
AMEN?

14:44.800 --> 14:46.932
HEY, AMEN.

14:46.934 --> 14:48.598
WHAT'S UP?
OH, THIS IS FRESH, MAN.

14:48.600 --> 14:49.798
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:49.800 --> 14:51.598
HEY, I APPRECIATE YOU
COMING THROUGH.

14:51.600 --> 14:52.932
HEY, NO PROBLEM, MAN.

14:52.934 --> 14:55.465
I FEEL KIND OF BAD
ABOUT THE OTHER DAY.

14:55.467 --> 14:58.598
NO, DON'T, DON'T.
I WAS TOTALLY IN MY FEELINGS.

14:58.600 --> 15:01.265
I WAS COMING OFF OF WHAT
HAPPENED WITH ME AND NIKKI.

15:01.267 --> 15:03.165
IT'S ALL GOOD.
THINGS LOOKING ANY BETTER.

15:03.167 --> 15:05.232
I KNOW SHE'S BEEN
STAYING WITH ZORA.

15:05.234 --> 15:06.732
YEAH, NOT REALLY.

15:06.734 --> 15:10.132
BUT WHEN THIS PLACE
OPENS UP, MAN,

15:10.134 --> 15:11.732
IT'S GOING TO BE
FULL OF HUNNIES.

15:11.734 --> 15:13.065
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOU KNOW WHAT I'M SAYING?

15:13.067 --> 15:14.665
RIGHT.
FULL OF THEM!

15:20.267 --> 15:22.665
YO, MAN, YOU ALRIGHT?

15:22.667 --> 15:24.798
YEAH. YEAH.

15:24.800 --> 15:26.265
WHATEVER.

15:26.267 --> 15:29.132
YOU KNOW, SHE WAS PROBABLY
JUST WATCHING OUT FOR ME

15:29.134 --> 15:30.265
WITH THE WHOLE MONEY THING,

15:30.267 --> 15:34.132
BUT IT'S ALL GOOD
'CAUSE I MOVED ON.

15:34.134 --> 15:35.732
ALREADY?
YEAH.

15:35.734 --> 15:36.998
OKAY. WITH WHO?

15:37.000 --> 15:39.831
I'M GOING TO LET YOU KNOW
WHEN IT'S SOLID.

15:39.833 --> 15:41.765
[ CHUCKLES ] FAIR ENOUGH.

15:41.767 --> 15:43.599
SO, THIS WHOLE
SCHOOL THING --

15:43.601 --> 15:46.065
EXCELLENCE PREP.
RIGHT.

15:46.067 --> 15:47.731
I TALKED TO MY PEOPLE.

15:47.733 --> 15:49.931
LET'S DO IT.

15:49.933 --> 15:52.131
ALRIGHT. LISTEN, MAN.
IT'S -- IT'S OKAY.

15:52.133 --> 15:55.465
I WAS JUST KIND OF IN MY OWN
FEELINGS WITH KERISSA, MAN,

15:55.467 --> 15:58.065
AND I REALLY SHOULDN'T HAVE EVEN
COME AT YOU LIKE THAT.

15:58.067 --> 15:59.798
HEY.

15:59.800 --> 16:01.732
I ALREADY SIGNED THE CHECK.

16:05.067 --> 16:07.932
OH, WOW. DANTE...

16:07.934 --> 16:09.532
I CAN'T ACCEPT THIS, MAN.

16:09.534 --> 16:10.865
YEAH, YOU CAN.

16:10.867 --> 16:13.798
YEAH. I FEEL BAD
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED --

16:13.800 --> 16:18.032
ME LOSING YOU AND YOUR JOBS.
BUT I NEED A FAVOR.

16:18.034 --> 16:19.665
OH, NO.

16:19.667 --> 16:20.798
YEAH. YOU KNOW.

16:20.800 --> 16:23.532
CAN YOUR WIFE, UM --
WHAT'S HER NAME?

16:23.534 --> 16:24.398
KERISSA.

16:24.400 --> 16:25.732
KERISSA?
YEAH. CAN ME AND HER

16:25.734 --> 16:29.798
DO SOME KIND OF PRESS-CONFERENCE
ANNOUNCEMENT SOON?

16:29.800 --> 16:32.198
BECAUSE I HAVE TO GET OFF
THAT BENCH, MAN,

16:32.200 --> 16:34.832
AND THE G.M. SAYS
THAT THIS IS A WAY TO DO IT.

16:34.834 --> 16:36.631
I'M SURE SHE COULD DO THAT.

16:36.633 --> 16:38.965
ALRIGHT, COOL. IT'S DONE.

16:41.467 --> 16:43.465
HEY, DEVON, HOLD ON.
OKAY.

16:43.467 --> 16:45.532
YO. GIVE THAT CHECK
TO KERISSA.

16:45.534 --> 16:47.499
SEE IF SHE DON'T SOFTEN UP.

16:47.501 --> 16:50.565
YOU MIGHT GET THE HIGH SCORE ON
THAT THING, OKAY? YOU FEEL ME?

16:50.567 --> 16:52.165
[Chuckling ] I DO.
ALRIGHT.

16:52.167 --> 16:53.232
THANK YOU, DANTE.

16:53.234 --> 16:55.798
HEY, I'M JUST A MAN.

16:55.800 --> 16:58.465
THANK JESUS.

16:58.467 --> 16:59.798
LET'S TALK.

16:59.800 --> 17:02.198
I NEED TWO OF THESE
BAD BOYS RIGHT HERE.

17:02.200 --> 17:06.598
A DINNER?
LIKE, A WHOLE DINNER?

17:06.600 --> 17:07.798
YEAH. SHE CAN HELP WITH BOB

17:07.800 --> 17:09.998
WHEN IT COMES TO MAKING YOU
ASSOCIATE PASTOR.

17:10.000 --> 17:11.398
WAIT.
SO IT'S UP TO BOB NOW?

17:11.400 --> 17:13.932
RELAX.
IT'S ALL GOING TO HAPPEN.

17:13.934 --> 17:17.398
BUT WHY NOT MAKE SURE
ALL OF OUR BASES ARE COVERED?

17:17.400 --> 17:18.798
IT'S JUST A DINNER.

17:18.800 --> 17:21.731
ALRIGHT.
DOES SHE KNOW ABOUT...

17:21.733 --> 17:23.399
YOU KNOW, GRACE?

17:23.401 --> 17:25.898
NO, NO.
AND WE DON'T WANT HER TO.

17:25.900 --> 17:27.898
WE WANT TO MAKE SURE
GRACE IS GONE

17:27.900 --> 17:29.965
BEFORE BOB CAN DO
ANYTHING ABOUT IT.

17:29.967 --> 17:31.899
GOT IT.

17:31.901 --> 17:33.965
WHAT'S THAT SMILE?

17:33.967 --> 17:37.232
I'M JUST THINKING ABOUT
WHERE I WANT TO EAT.

17:37.234 --> 17:39.565
I'LL DO IT IF IT'S SUSHI.

17:39.567 --> 17:46.531
♪♪

17:46.533 --> 17:54.332
♪♪

17:54.334 --> 17:55.532
IT JUST WENT TO VOICEMAIL.

17:55.534 --> 17:59.665
DAMN IT, A.J.
PICK UP THE PHONE.

17:59.667 --> 18:02.198
WAIT. WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

18:02.200 --> 18:05.598
HEY, LISTEN, IT'S ME.

18:05.600 --> 18:07.532
I KNOW I'M JUST SOME KID
FROM THE 'BURBS

18:07.534 --> 18:09.465
WHO DOESN'T KNOW ANYTHING,

18:09.467 --> 18:12.465
BUT RIGHT NOW, MY MOM
IS IN SERIOUS TROUBLE,

18:12.467 --> 18:16.198
AND SHE JUST NEEDS TO TALK
TO YOU TO FIND OUT THE TRUTH...

18:16.200 --> 18:17.998
OR SHE COULD GO TO JAIL.

18:18.000 --> 18:19.398
I KNOW THAT MIGHT
NOT MATTER TO YOU.

18:19.400 --> 18:22.865
I KNOW THAT YOU MIGHT STILL
HATE HER FOR NOT KEEPING YOU,

18:22.867 --> 18:28.265
FOR...ICING YOU OUT
WHEN YOU CAME LOOKING FOR HER.

18:28.267 --> 18:30.398
[ SIGHS ]

18:30.400 --> 18:32.299
BUT IF SHE GOES TO JAIL,
A.J...

18:35.800 --> 18:38.831
[Crying] I'M GOING TO LOSE
MY MOTHER,

18:38.833 --> 18:43.098
AND I HAVEN'T DONE ANYTHING.

18:43.100 --> 18:45.898
I DO NOT DESERVE THIS.

18:45.900 --> 18:47.399
IT'S NOT FAIR.

18:53.234 --> 18:57.598
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

18:57.600 --> 18:59.598
WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DO?

18:59.600 --> 19:07.465
I DON'T KNOW.

19:07.467 --> 19:09.198
I'M NOT GOING BACK
TO HAMPTON.

19:09.200 --> 19:10.665
WHAT?

19:10.667 --> 19:14.332
IT'S A SIX-WEEK PROGRAM.
I'VE DONE THREE WEEKS.

19:14.334 --> 19:16.932
I'LL JUST START BACK IN THE FALL
LIKE A NORMAL PERSON.

19:16.934 --> 19:19.332
NO, BABY.

19:19.334 --> 19:21.765
DON'T DO THAT.
I'M GOING TO BE FINE.

19:24.934 --> 19:33.632
MOM, IF I DON'T STAY FOR THIS,
WHAT WOULD I STAY FOR?

19:36.800 --> 19:40.865
YOU'RE MY MOM.

19:40.867 --> 19:42.999
I'M STAYING.

19:45.767 --> 19:50.198
♪♪

19:50.200 --> 19:51.998
HEY.

19:52.000 --> 19:54.198
WHAT?

19:54.200 --> 19:56.998
WELL, I'VE BEEN DEBATING
WHETHER I SHOULD TELL YOU THIS.

19:57.000 --> 19:59.398
I THOUGHT I MIGHT JUST WAIT
TO SEE WHAT HAPPENS,

19:59.400 --> 20:01.465
BUT...

20:01.467 --> 20:05.532
I'M FEELING FAIRLY CONFIDENT
THAT IT'LL WORK OUT.

20:05.534 --> 20:09.465
WHAT DID YOU DO, JAMES?

20:09.467 --> 20:11.532
WELL...

20:11.534 --> 20:14.132
I SPOKE TO CONNIE.

20:14.134 --> 20:17.532
I TRIED TO IMPRESS UPON HER
WHAT A DISASTER IT WOULD BE

20:17.534 --> 20:20.665
IF THE DEACONS WERE TO GO
ALONG WITH THIS PLAN.

20:20.667 --> 20:21.932
OH, SHE COULDN'T HEAR IT.

20:21.934 --> 20:24.332
YOU DID NOT TELL HER
YOU KNOW ABOUT THE BRIBE.

20:24.334 --> 20:25.798
TELL ME YOU DIDN'T.

20:25.800 --> 20:29.398
I HAD TO.
BUT I THINK IT WORKED!

20:29.400 --> 20:32.632
DID I NOT EXPLICITLY
PROHIBIT YOU FROM USING THAT?

20:32.634 --> 20:33.899
I HAD NO CHOICE!

20:33.901 --> 20:34.898
DID I NOT MAKE IT CLEAR

20:34.900 --> 20:36.465
THAT WIELDING A WEAPON
LIKE THAT

20:36.467 --> 20:37.865
COULD HURT US MORE
IN THE LONG RUN

20:37.867 --> 20:39.565
THAN IT CAN EVER HURT CONNIE?

20:39.567 --> 20:41.799
I MEAN, DIDN'T I LAY THAT
OUT CLEARLY?

20:41.801 --> 20:45.265
HOW CAN YOU BE SO WISE
ABOUT SO MANY THINGS

20:45.267 --> 20:47.465
AND SO FOOLISH
ABOUT OTHERS?

20:47.467 --> 20:49.732
HOW IS THAT POSSIBLE?

20:49.734 --> 20:52.065
I AM FLABBERGASTED.

20:52.067 --> 20:54.132
I'M TRYING TO GET YOU
YOUR CHURCH BACK, MAE.

20:54.134 --> 20:55.332
CAN YOU NOT SEE THAT?

20:55.334 --> 20:56.732
WELL, IF THE LOVE
YOU HAVE FOR ME

20:56.734 --> 20:58.398
IS SUCH THAT YOU DO
UNGODLY THINGS,

20:58.400 --> 21:00.465
IT'S NOT A GODLY LOVE.

21:00.467 --> 21:02.099
YOU'RE REALLY
GOING TO SAY THAT?

21:03.734 --> 21:07.132
[ SCOFFS ]

21:07.134 --> 21:09.798
NO, JAMES,
I DON'T WANT TO FIGHT.

21:09.800 --> 21:11.865
IF I DIDN'T HAVE YOU
RIGHT NOW,

21:11.867 --> 21:15.065
I WOULD BE DROWNING
IN A POOL OF HOPELESSNESS.

21:15.067 --> 21:19.431
OUR CHILDREN ARE ALL FLAILING
IN ONE WAY OR ANOTHER.

21:19.433 --> 21:21.499
OUR PAST HAS HUNTED US

21:21.501 --> 21:24.098
LIKE A PACK OF WOLVES
IN THE NIGHT.

21:24.100 --> 21:25.732
I...

21:29.100 --> 21:33.598
JAMES, I'M NOT JUDGING YOU.

21:33.600 --> 21:37.798
AND THANK YOU FOR CARING,
BUT...

21:37.800 --> 21:41.265
DON'T ASK ME TO PRETEND
NOT TO BE TERRIFIED

21:41.267 --> 21:43.532
BY HOW I THINK THIS MOVE
AGAINST CONNIE

21:43.534 --> 21:45.965
IS GOING TO BE OUR UNDOING.

21:48.600 --> 21:51.465
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

21:51.467 --> 21:52.998
TO MY PRAYER CLOSET.

21:53.000 --> 21:54.732
I THOUGHT I WAS DONE
FOR THE NIGHT, BUT, WELL,

21:54.734 --> 21:56.532
I'LL SEE YOU IN THE MORNING.

21:56.534 --> 21:59.032
♪♪

21:59.034 --> 22:02.265
I'M ASKING YOU FIRST
BECAUSE CHARITY'S PAYING

22:02.267 --> 22:03.532
ALL THAT MONEY TO KEVIN
FOR ALIMONY

22:03.534 --> 22:05.198
AND I THINK
SHE'S STILL MAD AT ME

22:05.200 --> 22:07.732
FOR NOT SUPPORTING HER
SILLY DREAM OF BEING A.P.

22:07.734 --> 22:09.132
OH, SHE'S MAD AT EVERYONE
RIGHT NOW.

22:09.134 --> 22:10.765
I WOULDN'T TAKE THAT
PERSONALLY.

22:10.767 --> 22:13.265
IS THIS SOMETHING THAT YOU
WOULD BE WILLING TO DO --

22:13.267 --> 22:15.665
EVEN ABLE TO DO?

22:15.667 --> 22:17.132
AND I'M SORRY FOR
BOTHERING YOU WITH THIS,

22:17.134 --> 22:19.265
WITH EVERYTHING YOU'RE GOING
THROUGH WITH A.J. RIGHT NOW.

22:19.267 --> 22:20.332
NO, IT'S OKAY.

22:20.334 --> 22:23.732
I JUST WANT TO MOVE ON.

22:23.734 --> 22:26.965
ARE YOU SURE THIS IS RIGHT
FOR YOU GUYS?

22:26.967 --> 22:29.831
I MEAN, I GUESS
IF I BUY YOU OUT,

22:29.833 --> 22:32.498
YOU CAN ALWAYS BUY YOUR SHARE
BACK, AND MINE, TOO.

22:32.500 --> 22:34.165
SO, YOU DO HAVE THE CASH?

22:34.167 --> 22:36.131
I HAVE SOME, YEAH.

22:36.133 --> 22:38.065
AND...

22:38.067 --> 22:39.732
MAYBE THIS IS WHY I HAVE IT.

22:39.734 --> 22:40.998
WHERE'D YOU GET IT?

22:41.000 --> 22:42.732
[ Chuckling ]
THAT'S A LONG STORY.

22:42.734 --> 22:45.499
BUT, KERISSA,
I HAVE TO BE HONEST.

22:45.501 --> 22:47.665
SOMETHING ABOUT THIS FEELS
RUSHED AND WEIRD TO ME.

22:47.667 --> 22:49.532
AM I WRONG?

22:49.534 --> 22:51.132
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

22:51.134 --> 22:53.532
LOOK, WHEN I MARRIED JACOB,

22:53.534 --> 22:56.665
SEEING THAT HE WAS
THE ONLY MALE IN THE FAMILY,

22:56.667 --> 22:59.065
I SAW US
IN THIS HOUSE FOREVER.

22:59.067 --> 23:00.132
I THINK WE ALL DID.

23:00.134 --> 23:02.265
BUT IT'S NOT WORKING OUT
LIKE THAT, GIGI.

23:02.267 --> 23:03.231
AND WITH THE WAY THINGS ARE

23:03.233 --> 23:04.765
BETWEEN ME AND YOUR MOTHER
RIGHT NOW,

23:04.767 --> 23:07.232
I'M NOT SURE I EVEN WANT
TO STAY IN THIS HOUSE.

23:07.234 --> 23:08.799
THAT BAD, HUH?

23:08.801 --> 23:10.999
I'M NOT PROUD TO SAY IT,
BUT, YEAH.

23:11.001 --> 23:14.532
WELL, HOW MUCH
DO YOU GUYS WANT?

23:14.534 --> 23:17.065
WELL, OUR SHARE IN THE HOUSE
IS EASILY WORTH A MILLION.

23:17.067 --> 23:19.365
OH.

23:19.367 --> 23:22.731
BUT WE WOULD TAKE $500,000.

23:22.733 --> 23:24.898
HONESTLY,
ANYTHING OVER $250,000

23:24.900 --> 23:26.965
WOULD BE LIKE
MANNA FROM HEAVEN.

23:26.967 --> 23:28.499
YOU REALLY WANT OUT?

23:28.501 --> 23:31.865
YEAH, LIKE JONAH
IN THE WHALE.

23:31.867 --> 23:33.031
♪♪

23:33.033 --> 23:35.432
SO, WHERE ARE WE GOING
TONIGHT?

23:35.434 --> 23:38.198
SOMEWHERE
WITH LOTS OF KNIVES.

23:38.200 --> 23:40.465
MM. SOUNDS PERFECT.

23:40.467 --> 23:43.432
WE NEED TO TALK PRIVATELY NOW.

23:49.267 --> 23:50.465
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

23:50.467 --> 23:52.131
WE'RE GOING TO HAVE TO
AMEND THE MOTION

23:52.133 --> 23:54.732
TO EXPAND
THE DEACON BOARD.

23:54.734 --> 23:56.732
WHY?

23:56.734 --> 24:00.265
[ SIGHS ]
JAMES KNOWS ABOUT THE...

24:00.267 --> 24:01.532
OH.

24:01.534 --> 24:02.899
HOW THE HELL
DID THAT HAPPEN?

24:02.901 --> 24:05.398
I CAN ONLY THINK KARINE.

24:05.400 --> 24:06.598
OH, THAT SNEAKY LITTLE --

24:06.600 --> 24:08.265
SO WE NEED TO AMEND
THE MOTION HOW?

24:08.267 --> 24:10.065
IT CAN'T BE A 50-50 SPLIT.

24:10.067 --> 24:12.198
THE CURRENT MEMBERS
OF THE BOARD

24:12.200 --> 24:14.532
HAVE TO MAINTAIN
MAJORITY CONTROL.

24:14.534 --> 24:18.099
OR WHAT?
THE BISHOP GOES PUBLIC?

24:18.101 --> 24:19.299
YES.

24:19.301 --> 24:22.399
SO, HE'S BLACKMAILING YOU?

24:22.401 --> 24:23.765
YES.

24:23.767 --> 24:28.465
WHAT DOES THE SPLIT HAVE TO BE
TO KEEP THE BLACKMAILER HAPPY?

24:28.467 --> 24:30.465
60-40.

24:32.934 --> 24:34.865
FINE.

24:34.867 --> 24:39.732
♪♪

24:39.734 --> 24:45.265
♪♪

24:45.267 --> 24:47.398
BLACKMAIL?

24:47.400 --> 24:50.365
WHO ARE THESE PEOPLE?

24:50.367 --> 24:58.465
♪♪

24:58.467 --> 25:01.798
YOU! LITTLE MISSY.

25:01.800 --> 25:03.165
YOU'RE FIRED.

25:06.667 --> 25:09.465
WHOSE SIDE ARE YOU ON?

25:09.467 --> 25:10.798
REALLY?

25:10.800 --> 25:11.999
WHY? WHAT HAPPENED?

25:12.001 --> 25:14.932
CONNIE SYKES...

25:14.934 --> 25:16.665
YOUR FATHER.

25:16.667 --> 25:20.465
♪♪

25:20.467 --> 25:23.832
I THOUGHT WE WERE ON
THE SAME PAGE HERE.

25:23.834 --> 25:26.731
LET'S MOVE THIS FORWARD.

25:26.733 --> 25:28.931
I'M SORRY.
IF I'M GOING TO HELP...

25:28.933 --> 25:30.865
[CHUCKLES]

25:30.867 --> 25:33.798
I NEED TO KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

25:33.800 --> 25:37.398
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

25:37.400 --> 25:38.665
NOTHING.

25:38.667 --> 25:47.598
♪♪

25:47.600 --> 25:51.499
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

25:54.101 --> 26:00.498
♪♪

26:00.500 --> 26:02.765
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

26:02.767 --> 26:10.132
♪♪

26:10.134 --> 26:12.131
I HAVE SOME GOOD NEWS.

26:12.133 --> 26:13.965
ME, TOO.

26:13.967 --> 26:16.031
YOU FIRST.

26:16.033 --> 26:17.232
♪♪

26:17.234 --> 26:18.998
Nikki: SERIOUSLY?!
Zora: WHAT'S WRONG NOW?

26:19.000 --> 26:21.398
THE SOFT OPENING FOR DANTE'S BAR
IS HAPPENING,

26:21.400 --> 26:23.398
AND HE DIDN'T EVEN
INVITE ME.

26:23.400 --> 26:25.065
WERE YOU EXPECTING HIM TO?

26:25.067 --> 26:26.665
UM, YEAH.
I DESIGNED THE PLACE.

26:26.667 --> 26:28.265
LOOK, JUST GO ANYWAY.

26:28.267 --> 26:32.598
NO, I WANT AN INVITATION.
I DESERVE IT. I DID EVERYTHING.

26:32.600 --> 26:34.665
THE BOY IS SO DAMN
DISRESPECTFUL.

26:34.667 --> 26:36.298
MAYBE HE'S JUST CONFLICTED.

26:36.300 --> 26:38.598
MAYBE YOU'RE JUST CONFUSED.
CAN YOU TWO JUST STOP?

26:38.600 --> 26:39.998
CONSTANT.

26:40.000 --> 26:41.932
YOU KNOW, I DON'T EVEN WANT
TO GO ANYWAY.

26:41.934 --> 26:45.198
BUCKETS -- IT'S THE DUMBEST NAME
FOR A SPORTS BAR EVER.

26:45.200 --> 26:47.598
I'M OUT OF HERE.

26:47.600 --> 26:51.332
WAIT. I-I THOUGHT WE WERE ALL
GOING TO ORDER IN.

26:51.334 --> 26:53.332
YEAH.

26:53.334 --> 26:55.332
I'M NOT HUNGRY.

26:55.334 --> 26:56.799
LATER.

27:00.734 --> 27:04.865
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

27:04.867 --> 27:07.132
YOU KNOW, MAYBE WE SHOULD,
LIKE, SHOW UP LATE --

27:07.134 --> 27:09.131
ACT LIKE WE DIDN'T KNOW
OR SOMETHING.

27:09.133 --> 27:12.332
YEAH, WE DON'T HAVE TO
DECIDE.

27:12.334 --> 27:13.899
NO, I THINK WE SHOULD GO.

27:13.901 --> 27:15.032
I AGREE.

27:15.034 --> 27:16.498
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:16.500 --> 27:17.698
OKAY.

27:17.700 --> 27:19.598
WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO WEAR?
I DON'T KNOW.

27:19.600 --> 27:21.665
[ SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

27:21.667 --> 27:24.332
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

27:24.334 --> 27:27.465
OOH. SUSHI AND STEAK.

27:27.467 --> 27:28.932
NICELY PLAYED.

27:28.934 --> 27:31.532
WELL, I'M GLAD YOU TWO
ARE SO HAPPY.

27:31.534 --> 27:34.232
IT IS SO RARE TO FIND A MAN
WHO CAN SATISFY ONE WOMAN,

27:34.234 --> 27:35.898
LET ALONE TWO.

27:35.900 --> 27:39.365
HE DOES HAVE A GIFT
IN PLEASING OTHERS. THAT'S TRUE.

27:39.367 --> 27:42.098
DON'T I KNOW IT?
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:42.100 --> 27:45.332
SO, HOW DID YOU TWO MEET?

27:45.334 --> 27:47.598
I MEAN, I KNOW HOW YOU MET,
BUT HOW DID YOU MEET?

27:47.600 --> 27:49.065
WHAT, WAS THE MEET CUTE?

27:49.067 --> 27:51.131
IT'S A FUNNY STORY, ACTUALLY.

27:51.133 --> 27:52.399
YEAH. HANG ON A SECOND.

27:52.401 --> 27:55.865
WHAT DID YOU MEAN BY,
"DON'T I KNOW IT?"

27:55.867 --> 27:57.832
I THINK I PUT MY FOOT IN IT.

27:57.834 --> 28:00.865
SHE MEANS SHE'S WATCHED ME
BE AT BOB'S BECK AND CALL

28:00.867 --> 28:03.399
FOR...20 YEARS NOW.

28:03.401 --> 28:05.465
DOES SHE NOT KNOW?

28:05.467 --> 28:07.798
JUDEE, YOU KNOW
SHE DOESN'T KNOW.

28:07.800 --> 28:09.498
WHAT DON'T I KNOW?

28:09.500 --> 28:11.832
WELL, IT'S NOT MINE TO SAY.

28:15.201 --> 28:17.765
I'M ABOUT TO GRAB ONE OF THESE
KNIVES LIKE A NINJA

28:17.767 --> 28:20.065
AND TAKE A SLICE
OUT OF BOTH OF YOU.

28:20.067 --> 28:22.165
WHAT DON'T I KNOW?

28:28.467 --> 28:31.498
[ SIGHS CONTENTEDLY ]

28:31.500 --> 28:33.698
[ SIGHS ] YOU COULD BUY
THAT HOUSE NOW.

28:33.700 --> 28:35.698
YEAH. FINALLY.

28:35.700 --> 28:38.198
GROW THAT SCHOOL.

28:38.200 --> 28:40.532
HMM.

28:40.534 --> 28:41.632
THIS HAS BEEN A GOOD DAY
FOR YOU.

28:41.634 --> 28:44.998
MM. IT'S GOING TO BE AN EVEN
BETTER NIGHT FOR YOU.

28:45.000 --> 28:47.265
REALLY?
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:47.267 --> 28:50.099
YEAH, REALLY.
REALLY AND THEN SOME.

28:55.600 --> 28:58.398
WAIT. COME ON, NOW.

28:58.400 --> 29:00.198
YOU KNOW YOU GOT TO GIVE
A BROTHER A MINUTE.

29:00.200 --> 29:01.865
MM-HMM. [ CHUCKLES ]

29:01.867 --> 29:03.299
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

29:03.301 --> 29:05.699
OHH.

29:05.701 --> 29:06.898
ALRIGHT.

29:06.900 --> 29:09.232
UH-OH. OKAY. THAT WORKS.

29:09.234 --> 29:11.165
YOU CAN'T STEP DOWN.

29:11.167 --> 29:13.798
YOU CAN'T SURRENDER
TO THIS MAN'S MENDACITY.

29:13.800 --> 29:17.198
WHAT IF PHIL TAKES THIS PROOF,
WHATEVER IT IS, TO THE COPS?

29:17.200 --> 29:19.065
AND WHAT ABOUT
CHARITY'S MENDACITY?

29:19.067 --> 29:21.332
OH, SHE'S JUST A HELPLESS PAWN
IN ALL OF THIS.

29:21.334 --> 29:24.665
AND THIS PROOF
THAT PHIL SAYS HE HAS,

29:24.667 --> 29:26.865
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT IT IS?

29:26.867 --> 29:28.932
I HAVE A FEELING IT HAS
SOMETHING TO DO WITH CHARITY

29:28.934 --> 29:31.598
AND THAT NIGHT THAT
A.J. CAME TO VISIT.

29:31.600 --> 29:34.798
BUT SHE WILL NOT ADMIT THAT
SHE KNOWS ANYTHING ABOUT IT.

29:34.800 --> 29:35.865
I'M GOING TO KILL HIM.

29:35.867 --> 29:38.065
HOW ABOUT KILLING CHARITY, HUH?

29:38.067 --> 29:41.732
GIGI, SHE'S SO HYPNOTIZED
BY THAT SCOUNDREL'S ATTENTION,

29:41.734 --> 29:44.465
I'M SURPRISED
SHE CAN STILL TIE HER SHOES.

29:44.467 --> 29:47.231
REMIND ME TO COME BACK NEXT TIME
AS THE YOUNGEST DAUGHTER.

29:47.233 --> 29:50.765
OH, REINCARNATION'S
A LIE OF THE DEVIL.

29:50.767 --> 29:52.432
I WAS JOKING.

29:52.434 --> 29:54.032
FROM THE SOUND
OF WHAT YOU'VE TOLD ME,

29:54.034 --> 29:57.632
AND FORGIVE ME
FOR SEEMING COLD,

29:57.634 --> 29:59.432
A.J.'S GUILTY.

29:59.434 --> 30:01.932
YOU DON'T KNOW
THAT HE IS GUILTY.

30:01.934 --> 30:04.131
BUT WHAT WOULD YOU DO
IF HE WAS?

30:04.133 --> 30:05.732
I'D STEP DOWN.

30:05.734 --> 30:09.865
[ SIGHS ]

30:09.867 --> 30:11.332
AND IF HE WAS INNOCENT?

30:16.934 --> 30:18.798
WELL, I'D STAY AND FIGHT,

30:18.800 --> 30:21.465
BECAUSE THEN AT LEAST
THERE WOULD BE A CHANCE

30:21.467 --> 30:23.865
THAT I COULD GET HIM
EXONERATED.

30:23.867 --> 30:24.932
I'M ABOUT TO HAVE
A STROKE.

30:24.934 --> 30:26.532
James: NO, WAIT.
WELL, GIGI'S RIGHT.

30:26.534 --> 30:29.765
NOW, IF HE DID IT, WE DON'T WANT
THE POLICE REOPENING THE CASE.

30:29.767 --> 30:31.565
WE CAN'T RISK SENDING
THE BOY BACK TO THE JAIL.

30:31.567 --> 30:34.965
HE'D BE THERE FOR DECADES.

30:34.967 --> 30:37.332
YOU DON'T WANT TO BE
THE CAUSE OF THAT, DO YOU?

30:39.601 --> 30:41.131
THIS HAPPENED BECAUSE OF YOU.

30:41.133 --> 30:42.598
WHAT?!

30:42.600 --> 30:45.998
IF THE BOY GOES TO JAIL,
HALF THE BLAME LIES WITH YOU.

30:46.000 --> 30:47.365
HOW DOES THAT WORK?

30:47.367 --> 30:48.865
OH, DO YOU THINK
IT'S A COINCIDENCE

30:48.867 --> 30:51.198
THAT YOUR DAUGHTER
IS FACING THIS KIND OF
SITUATION RIGHT NOW

30:51.200 --> 30:53.332
NOT A DAY, NOT 24 HOURS,

30:53.334 --> 30:54.732
AFTER YOU DID
THE SAME THING TO CONNIE?

30:54.734 --> 30:56.632
WHAT DID YOU DO?

30:56.634 --> 30:57.831
DISOBEYED ME.

30:57.833 --> 30:59.498
AND DON'T YOU MAKE
THAT MISTAKE.

30:59.500 --> 31:00.865
YOU LISTEN TO ME.

31:00.867 --> 31:03.565
OH, I'M LISTENING.
WE'RE ALL LISTENING, MAMA.

31:03.567 --> 31:06.798
GOOD. YOU CANNOT STEP DOWN.

31:06.800 --> 31:09.065
YOU NEED TO GET UP
IN THAT PULPIT ON SUNDAY

31:09.067 --> 31:10.398
AND TELL YOUR STORY,

31:10.400 --> 31:14.065
ALL THE WAY UP TO PHIL DEMARS
AND WHAT HE'S DOING,

31:14.067 --> 31:16.732
AND LET THE PEOPLE
OF THIS CHURCH DECIDE.

31:16.734 --> 31:18.665
TELL THEM THAT SHE LIED
TO THE POLICE?

31:18.667 --> 31:22.565
OH, THERE IS NOT A MOTHER
IN THOSE PEWS

31:22.567 --> 31:24.465
THAT WOULDN'T UNDERSTAND.

31:24.467 --> 31:25.532
AND WHAT ABOUT THE POLICE?

31:25.534 --> 31:27.732
THEY'LL GO AFTER HIM AGAIN --
AND HER.

31:27.734 --> 31:30.465
OH, IF THEY ACTUALLY CHARGED HER
FOR THIS GARBAGE,

31:30.467 --> 31:32.198
I WOULD EAT MY HAT.

31:32.200 --> 31:33.998
WHICH ONE?

31:34.000 --> 31:38.665
AND AS FOR A.J., THE TWO OF YOU
WANT TO KEEP HIM OUT OF JAIL.

31:38.667 --> 31:41.865
BUT WHAT USE
WILL HIS FREEDOM BE, GIGI,

31:41.867 --> 31:45.332
IF HE DID IT
AND KNOWS THAT HE DID...

31:45.334 --> 31:51.332
IF HE MISSES THIS CHANCE TO KNOW
THAT HIS SOUL IS REAL?

31:51.334 --> 31:54.465
THIS WORLD IS JUST
A WAITING ROOM FOR THE NEXT,

31:54.467 --> 31:58.199
SO LET HIM FACE
HIS FACTS NOW, GIGI.

31:58.201 --> 32:01.865
AND YOUR TASK...

32:01.867 --> 32:03.465
IS TO FACE YOURS.

32:03.467 --> 32:05.131
YOU GET UP THERE ON SUNDAY,

32:05.133 --> 32:07.198
YOU MAKE A STAND,

32:07.200 --> 32:09.598
YOU SPEAK YOUR OWN TRUTH,

32:09.600 --> 32:11.198
AND YOU WIN.

32:11.200 --> 32:17.199
♪♪

32:17.201 --> 32:20.198
YOU DO
WHAT'S BEST FOR YOUR SON.

32:20.200 --> 32:21.765
THANK YOU, DADDY.

32:25.667 --> 32:28.799
YOU DO WHAT'S BEST
FOR YOUR SOUL.

32:31.867 --> 32:35.065
AND EVERYTHING ELSE IS NOISE.

32:35.067 --> 32:42.598
♪♪

32:42.600 --> 32:50.032
♪♪

32:53.367 --> 32:56.432
[ MAN RAPPING INDISTINCTLY ]

32:58.700 --> 33:00.165
I DID GOOD.

33:00.167 --> 33:01.532
YOU DID.

33:01.534 --> 33:03.332
[ RAPPING CONTINUES ]

33:03.334 --> 33:05.965
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

33:08.601 --> 33:10.765
THAT'S HER, ISN'T IT?

33:10.767 --> 33:12.799
[ RAPPING CONTINUES ]

33:15.300 --> 33:18.132
NIKKI, WAIT. NIKKI.

33:20.400 --> 33:22.365
NOT HUNGRY, HUH?

33:22.367 --> 33:23.965
LOOKS LIKE YOU'RE HUNGRY
FOR SOMETHING.

33:23.967 --> 33:26.699
YO, WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

33:26.701 --> 33:28.798
MAN, DANG. MY TEAMS --
THEY MESSING UP.

33:28.800 --> 33:30.798
THERE'S SUPPOSED
TO BE A LIST.

33:30.800 --> 33:31.932
I<i> AM</i> THE LIST.

33:31.934 --> 33:33.665
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

33:33.667 --> 33:36.532
I DON'T KNOW.
I MUST BE CONFUSED.

33:36.534 --> 33:38.132
WHEN I YANK THAT PONYTAIL
OUT YOUR HEAD,

33:38.134 --> 33:39.432
YOU'RE GOING TO BE
PERPLEXED, BITCH.

33:39.434 --> 33:42.198
HEY, HEY, HEY.
YOU NEED TO BACK UP, A'IGHT?

33:42.200 --> 33:43.998
YOU'RE NOT EVEN SUPPOSED TO BE
HERE ANYWAY, BRUH.

33:44.000 --> 33:45.532
NIKKI, LET'S JUST GO.
COME ON.

33:45.534 --> 33:48.798
"BRUH"? SO YOU'RE REALLY GOING
TO DO ME LIKE THIS, DANTE?

33:48.800 --> 33:49.798
HE IS.

33:49.800 --> 33:50.931
BITCH, BACK THE HELL UP.

33:50.933 --> 33:52.932
NO,<i> YOU</i> BACK THE HELL UP.
YOU GUYS, STOP.

33:52.934 --> 33:56.198
WHAT ARE YOU GUYS DOING?!
COME ON!

33:56.200 --> 33:57.532
Nikki: GET OFF ME.
GO RIGHT NOW.

33:57.534 --> 33:59.098
DON'T TOUCH ME.
DON'T TOUCH ME.

33:59.100 --> 34:02.198
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

34:02.200 --> 34:03.965
I'M GONNA CATCH Y'ALL
LATER.

34:08.967 --> 34:10.898
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

34:10.900 --> 34:12.832
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

34:31.200 --> 34:33.265
GOT ANYTHING TO SAY?

34:33.267 --> 34:35.331
IT WAS A LONG TIME AGO.

34:35.333 --> 34:38.332
WE STAYED FRIENDS,
FOR OBVIOUS REASONS, EVER SINCE.

34:38.334 --> 34:39.998
IT'S NOTHING.
WHY KEEP IT A SECRET, THEN?

34:40.000 --> 34:41.265
IT WASN'T A SECRET.

34:41.267 --> 34:44.165
SUCH OLD NEWS,
I DIDN'T THINK IT MATTERED.

34:44.167 --> 34:47.799
AWW.

34:47.801 --> 34:49.265
YOU'RE CUTE
WHEN YOU'RE JEALOUS.

34:49.267 --> 34:50.865
YEAH?

34:50.867 --> 34:52.731
WELL, YOU'RE UGLY
WHEN YOU'RE DUMB.

34:52.733 --> 34:55.332
I'VE THROWN MY WHOLE LIFE
IN THE GARBAGE FOR YOU,

34:55.334 --> 34:58.865
AND NOW I'M LIKE,
"I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHO YOU ARE."

34:58.867 --> 35:00.465
YOU WANT TO KNOW WHY? HMM?

35:00.467 --> 35:02.065
I'M NOT SURE I DO
ANYMORE NOW.

35:02.067 --> 35:03.265
YOU WANT TO KNOW WHO AM I?

35:03.267 --> 35:06.131
ALRIGHT.

35:06.133 --> 35:08.299
HERE.

35:08.301 --> 35:09.765
WHAT IS THIS?

35:09.767 --> 35:11.832
THE KEY TO MY APARTMENT.
KEEP IT.

35:11.834 --> 35:13.798
GO THERE WHENEVER
YOU WANT TO LOOK AROUND.

35:13.800 --> 35:16.265
BUT I'LL WARN YOU --
YOU'RE GOING TO SEE

35:16.267 --> 35:18.732
A COUPLE OF PICTURES
ON THE REFRIGERATOR OF...

35:18.734 --> 35:20.332
YOU

35:20.334 --> 35:24.732
THAT I PRINTED THE DAY
AFTER WE MET AND...

35:24.734 --> 35:26.665
WELL, LESS THAN A PAGE
IN MY PRAYER JOURNAL

35:26.667 --> 35:28.598
OF ALL THE THINGS
I WANT TO DO FOR YOU

35:28.600 --> 35:30.732
ONCE -- ONCE...

35:30.734 --> 35:32.698
ONCE WHAT?

35:32.700 --> 35:34.432
ONCE A STUPID NIGHT LIKE THIS
IS SO FAR BACK

35:34.434 --> 35:37.398
IN THE REARVIEW MIRROR,
WE CAN'T EVEN SEE IT.

35:37.400 --> 35:39.932
IT'S YOURS.

35:39.934 --> 35:42.665
I ONLY SAID YES TO THE DINNER
TO GET JUDEE ON OUR SIDE

35:42.667 --> 35:46.632
BECAUSE IT'S...
GOTTEN SO I --

35:46.634 --> 35:49.132
I CAN'T EVEN THINK ABOUT RUNNING
THIS CHURCH WITHOUT YOU

35:49.134 --> 35:52.165
OR...DOING ANYTHING ELSE,
FOR THAT MATTER.

35:52.167 --> 35:55.598
♪♪

35:55.600 --> 35:57.398
YOU REALLY LIKE ME,
DON'T YOU?

35:57.400 --> 36:01.065
LIKE YOU? [ CHUCKLES ]

36:01.067 --> 36:04.465
CHARITY...

36:04.467 --> 36:07.265
I LOVE YOU.

36:07.267 --> 36:11.465
OKAY? I-I LOVE YOU.

36:11.467 --> 36:14.765
I LOVE YOU. [ CHUCKLES ]

36:14.767 --> 36:22.999
♪♪

36:23.001 --> 36:25.065
SO, WHAT WAS
LAST NIGHT ABOUT?

36:28.600 --> 36:29.998
YOU TELL ME.

36:30.000 --> 36:31.465
[ CHUCKLES ]

36:31.467 --> 36:34.398
HOW AM I SUPPOSED TO EXPLAIN
SOMETHING THAT YOU DID TO YOU?

36:34.400 --> 36:37.332
ARE YOU DRINKING
STUPID JUICE OUT THE MUG?

36:37.334 --> 36:39.265
WHAT I'M DRINKING IS "I DON'T
CARE WHAT YOU OR NIKKI

36:39.267 --> 36:41.698
OR ANYBODY ELSE
HAS TO SAY ABOUT ME" JUICE.

36:41.700 --> 36:43.532
[ SIGHS ]
YOU HAVE A PROBLEM.

36:43.534 --> 36:46.198
YOU KNOW THAT?
LIKE, A REAL SERIOUS PROBLEM.

36:46.200 --> 36:47.865
DANTE BROKE UP WITH NIKKI.

36:47.867 --> 36:49.465
I DON'T KNOW HER,
AND I DON'T WANT TO KNOW HER,

36:49.467 --> 36:51.332
SO WHY SHOULD I CARE?

36:51.334 --> 36:53.998
YOU SHOULD CARE BECAUSE
YOU HAVE NO FRIENDS

36:54.000 --> 36:56.198
AND YOU'RE NOT GOING TO MAKE
ANY NEW FRIENDS

36:56.200 --> 36:57.865
IF YOU KEEP ON
ROLLING YOUR EYES AT GIRLS

36:57.867 --> 36:59.465
THAT COULD BE YOUR FRIEND

36:59.467 --> 37:01.132
AND THEN TURNING AROUND
AND BATTING YOUR EYES

37:01.134 --> 37:02.665
AT THE GUYS
THAT THEY'VE BEEN WITH.

37:02.667 --> 37:05.798
I CAN DO WHATEVER I WANT
WITH WHOEVER I WANT. I'M GROWN.

37:05.800 --> 37:07.665
YOU A HO.
THAT'S WHAT YOU ARE.

37:07.667 --> 37:10.765
AND I'M SO HAPPY
YOU'RE GOING BACK TO SCHOOL.

37:10.767 --> 37:13.632
I'M NOT.

37:13.634 --> 37:16.832
ACTUALLY,
I'VE DECIDED TO STAY.

37:16.834 --> 37:18.032
AND IT'S GOING TO BE GREAT.

37:21.267 --> 37:24.065
Mae:
GOOD MORNING, SOPHIA.

37:24.067 --> 37:25.032
MORNING, EVERYBODY.

37:25.034 --> 37:27.098
KIND OF SHORT.
MORNING, ZORA.

37:27.100 --> 37:30.398
HEY, BABY DOLL.
OOH! THIS LOOKS SO GOOD!

37:30.400 --> 37:31.598
I'M STARVING.

37:31.600 --> 37:33.732
OH, YOU ARE SHARP!

37:33.734 --> 37:36.065
YEAH, JUST LIKE DADDY.
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:36.067 --> 37:37.932
GO AHEAD DOWNSTAIRS,
OKAY?

37:37.934 --> 37:39.565
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

37:39.567 --> 37:44.132
[ GROANS ]

37:44.134 --> 37:47.198
PLEASE STOP CALLING ME,
PLEASE.

37:47.200 --> 37:51.732
I HAVE SOME NEWS ABOUT THE HOUSE
YOU MIGHT FIND VERY INTERESTING.

37:51.734 --> 37:53.198
WE DIDN'T GET THE HOUSE.

37:53.200 --> 37:55.665
NOT THAT HOUSE,
THE HOUSE YOU STANDING IN --

37:55.667 --> 37:58.598
THE ONE THAT YOU COULD VERY WELL
BE THE OWNER OF ONE DAY.

37:58.600 --> 38:04.265
♪♪

38:04.267 --> 38:10.665
♪♪

38:10.667 --> 38:13.932
I HOPE I DIDN'T CAUSE
ANY TROUBLE LAST NIGHT.

38:13.934 --> 38:16.265
I THOUGHT SHE KNEW.

38:16.267 --> 38:19.598
NO, YOU DIDN'T.
BUT THAT'S OKAY.

38:19.600 --> 38:21.165
YOU SHOWED HER WHO'S BOSS?

38:21.167 --> 38:24.265
NO, BUT I PUT OUT THE FIRE
YOU'RE TRYING TO START.

38:24.267 --> 38:27.732
GREAT, BECAUSE WE'RE GOING
TO BE NEEDING HER HELP
WITH SOMETHING SOON.

38:27.734 --> 38:29.331
I'M LISTENING.

38:29.333 --> 38:32.665
IN CALVARY'S BYLAWS, WHICH I WAS
FINALLY ABLE TO READ LAST NIGHT,

38:32.667 --> 38:35.465
IT STATES THAT THE MOST SENIOR
GREENLEAF EMPLOYED AT CALVARY

38:35.467 --> 38:38.198
CAN ALWAYS CAST THE TIE-BREAKING
VOTE IN BOARD DISPUTES.

38:38.200 --> 38:39.332
I'M NOT SURE I FOLLOW.

38:39.334 --> 38:40.798
IF WE GET THOSE 10 SEATS
ON THE BOARD

38:40.800 --> 38:42.465
AND THE CHURCH KEEPS 12,

38:42.467 --> 38:44.465
WE STILL HAVE CONNIE WITH US.

38:44.467 --> 38:46.031
IT'LL BE A TIE.

38:46.033 --> 38:48.332
WHEN WE VOTE FOR WHAT?

38:48.334 --> 38:51.531
THAT'S FOR ME TO KNOW
AND YOU TO FIND OUT.

38:51.533 --> 38:53.599
BUT KEEP HER HAPPY.

38:53.601 --> 38:57.832
WE'RE GOING TO BE NEEDING
HER VOTE.

38:57.834 --> 39:03.598
♪♪

39:03.600 --> 39:07.398
♪ THIS MORNING
WHEN I ROSE, YEAH ♪

39:07.400 --> 39:10.198
♪ I DIDN'T HAVE NO DOUBT ♪

39:10.200 --> 39:13.998
♪ OH, THIS MORNING
WHEN I ROSE, YEAH ♪

39:14.000 --> 39:16.332
♪ I DIDN'T HAVE NO DOUBT ♪

39:16.334 --> 39:20.998
♪ HEY!
THIS MORNING WHEN I ROSE, YEAH ♪

39:21.000 --> 39:23.598
♪ I DIDN'T HAVE NO DOUBT ♪

39:23.600 --> 39:25.332
♪ I KNOW THE LORD ♪

39:25.334 --> 39:27.198
♪ WILL TAKE CARE OF ME ♪

39:27.200 --> 39:28.198
♪ I KNOW THE LORD ♪

39:28.200 --> 39:29.598
♪ WILL PROVIDE FOR ME ♪

39:29.600 --> 39:31.565
♪ AND HE WILL ♪

39:31.567 --> 39:34.499
♪ LEAD AND GUIDE ME
ALL THE WAY ♪

39:34.501 --> 39:37.932
♪ YES, ALL THE WAY ♪
♪ ALL THE WAY ♪

39:37.934 --> 39:39.532
HALLELUJAH!

39:39.534 --> 39:42.732
SOMEBODY GIVE A SHOUT OF PRAISE!

39:42.734 --> 39:45.799
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

39:53.367 --> 39:56.965
AMEN! GOOD MORNING, CALVARY!

39:56.967 --> 39:58.165
All: GOOD MORNING!

39:58.167 --> 40:00.732
IT FEELS SO GOOD
TO BE WORSHIPING

40:00.734 --> 40:02.798
IN GOD'S HOUSE WITH YOU TODAY.
AMEN?

40:02.800 --> 40:03.998
All: AMEN!

40:04.000 --> 40:05.798
AMEN. WELL, LET'S GET RIGHT
TO THE REASON

40:05.800 --> 40:08.965
WHY WE ARE HERE TODAY --
THE WORD OF GOD.

40:08.967 --> 40:10.198
AMEN?
YES, YES!

40:10.200 --> 40:12.998
OKAY. TURN WITH ME
IN YOUR BIBLES, IF YOU WOULD,

40:13.000 --> 40:17.532
TO LUKE 22:40.

